dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Insurance. My name is Joe Perry. May I please have your name?
Hi, my name is Abigail Robinson.
Thank you, Abigail. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is five six eight seven two.
Thank you, Abigail. Also, can you confirm your date of birth for security purposes?
My date of birth is zero four one five one nine eight nine.
Great, thank you for verifying. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today regarding your policy?
I have a question about adding a new vehicle to my coverage.
Of course, I'd be happy to help with that. Let's go ahead and discuss the details. Thank you for reaching out, Abigail. Please let me know if you need anything else.
Thank you for your time. Have a great day!
